# Smart Inventory Assets System - Modules Design Document

## Overview
This document outlines the modular architecture of the Smart Inventory Assets System, detailing all system modules, their responsibilities, and interactions.

## System Architecture

### Core Modules

#### 1. Authentication & Authorization Module
**File:** `backend/modules/auth.js`
**Responsibilities:**
- User authentication (login, logout, session management)
- Role-based access control (RBAC)
- JWT token management
- Password security and reset functionality
- Multi-factor authentication support

**Key Features:**
- Secure password hashing with bcrypt
- JWT-based stateless authentication
- Role hierarchy: Super Admin > Admin > Manager > User > Guest
- Permission-based access control
- Session timeout and refresh token management

**API Endpoints:**
- `POST /auth/login` - User authentication
- `POST /auth/logout` - User logout
- `POST /auth/refresh` - Token refresh
- `POST /auth/forgot-password` - Password reset request
- `POST /auth/reset-password` - Password reset confirmation

---

#### 2. User Management Module
**File:** `backend/modules/users.js`
**Responsibilities:**
- User profile management
- User role assignment and management
- User activity tracking
- Department and team management
- User preferences and settings

**Key Features:**
- CRUD operations for user accounts
- Bulk user operations
- User import/export functionality
- Activity logging and audit trails
- User profile customization

**API Endpoints:**
- `GET /users` - List users with pagination
- `POST /users` - Create new user
- `GET /users/:id` - Get user details
- `PUT /users/:id` - Update user information
- `DELETE /users/:id` - Deactivate/delete user
- `GET /users/activity` - User activity logs

---

#### 3. Inventory Management Module
**File:** `backend/modules/inventory.js`
**Responsibilities:**
- Product catalog management
- Stock level tracking
- Barcode/QR code generation
- Product categorization
- Supplier management integration

**Key Features:**
- Real-time inventory tracking
- Multi-warehouse support
- Batch/lot tracking
- Expiration date management
- Low stock alerts
- Stock adjustment history

**API Endpoints:**
- `GET /inventory` - List inventory items
- `POST /inventory` - Add new product
- `PUT /inventory/:id` - Update product
- `DELETE /inventory/:id` - Remove product
- `POST /inventory/adjust` - Stock adjustment
- `GET /inventory/low-stock` - Low stock items

---

#### 4. Assets Management Module
**File:** `backend/modules/assets.js`
**Responsibilities:**
- Asset registration and tracking
- Asset lifecycle management
- Maintenance scheduling
- Depreciation calculation
- Asset assignment and transfer

**Key Features:**
- Complete asset lifecycle tracking
- Maintenance scheduling and reminders
- Asset valuation and depreciation
- QR code generation for assets
- Asset audit trails
- Multi-location asset tracking

**API Endpoints:**
- `GET /assets` - List all assets
- `POST /assets` - Register new asset
- `PUT /assets/:id` - Update asset details
- `DELETE /assets/:id` - Remove asset
- `POST /assets/:id/assign` - Assign asset to user
- `GET /assets/maintenance` - Maintenance schedule
- `GET /assets/overview` - Asset analytics

---

#### 5. Sales Management Module
**File:** `backend/modules/sales.js`
**Responsibilities:**
- Sales order processing
- Customer management
- Invoice generation
- Payment processing
- Sales analytics

**Key Features:**
- Quotation to sales order conversion
- Multiple payment methods support
- Tax calculation
- Discount management
- Sales commission tracking
- Customer credit management

**API Endpoints:**
- `GET /sales` - List sales transactions
- `POST /sales` - Create sales order
- `GET /sales/:id` - Get sales details
- `PUT /sales/:id` - Update sales order
- `POST /sales/:id/invoice` - Generate invoice
- `GET /sales/analytics` - Sales analytics

---

#### 6. Purchase Management Module
**File:** `backend/modules/purchases.js`
**Responsibilities:**
- Purchase order creation
- Supplier management
- Goods receipt processing
- Purchase invoice management
- Expense tracking

**Key Features:**
- Purchase order approval workflow
- Supplier performance tracking
- Goods receipt verification
- Purchase return processing
- Budget tracking
- Multi-currency support

**API Endpoints:**
- `GET /purchases` - List purchase orders
- `POST /purchases` - Create purchase order
- `PUT /purchases/:id` - Update purchase order
- `POST /purchases/:id/receive` - Record goods receipt
- `GET /purchases/suppliers` - Supplier list
- `GET /purchases/analytics` - Purchase analytics

---

#### 7. Financial Management Module
**File:** `backend/modules/financial.js`
**Responsibilities:**
- Payment processing
